Package edu.uky.games.physics_game.collision

Class ListNode

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.games.physics_game.collision.ListNode
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListNode.Bottom, ListNode.Left, ListNode.Right, ListNode.Top
public abstract class ListNode extends Object
Represents a single edge of one rigid body's axis-aligned bounding box along one dimension. Because this engine deals with 2D space, there are found possible types of edges: top, bottom, left, and right.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
